{"tid":1643290,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（緊急）好似發現左一個政府大陰謀","createTime":"2019-10-10T05:20:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T09:05:03.000Z","uid":304769,"like":18,"dislike":212,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"6e0e29b06121330aeb9ee35df7f72f920f7e9408","tid":1643290,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:20:49.000Z","msg":"大家有冇發覺呢幾日地鐵早收咗<br />\n 真係好似乜q都靜曬 <br />\n我懷疑呢個係政府嘅模擬宵禁<br />\n為用緊急法出宵禁鋪路<br />\n<br />\n而且呢個又係一個公我贏字你輸的局面<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">情景1.如果呢幾日我地靜曬，佢好有理由話宵禁有用<br />\n<br />\n情景2.如果呢幾日我地出黎抗爭，佢又可以話有宵禁的必要</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家有有何拆解之法？"},{"pid":"383de20298608fcb0aaacdb91f29e42c5b3b92a2","tid":1643290,"uid":232671,"like":166,"dislike":1,"score":165,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:22:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有人一早講咗, 擺到明就係宵禁啦...佢唔會講明嫁..."},{"pid":"09362ea68b736b3f7d8f0be722bd8dd999477fc5","tid":1643290,"uid":59192,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:23:17.000Z","msg":"宵禁好有用<br />\n咁繼續<br />\n當佢一解番就<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b23eae7f7adbc10c176ee8f01ca5a2b940fcf85","tid":1643290,"uid":106094,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:24:07.000Z","msg":"你仲理鳩佢噏乜鳩 🤷🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n佢話你暴徒你係咪就係暴徒呀？<br />\n要出街就出啦"},{"pid":"8ec23c68f703c1842053639337f7163f7fa31521","tid":1643290,"uid":152976,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:27:39.000Z","msg":"攬炒之路 宵禁炒起班商家佬 順勢搞埋金融 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇咩好需要拆解 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282de27b2d4ec42c39e8d352c7642555b0d35dcd","tid":1643290,"uid":228955,"like":12,"